<document>
 <properties>
  <title>Hippo CMS Admin Tour</title>
 </properties>
 <body>
  <section name="Hippo CMS Admin Tour">
   <span class='shortdesc'>To get introduced to the role of CMS administrator,
    take the following tour.</span>

   <blockquote>
    <table>

     <tr>
      <td>Browser</td>
      <td>
       <span class='web-48 icon-48'/>
      </td>
      <td>
        Open the Hippo CMS site
        <a href="http://localhost:8080/cms/">http://localhost:8080/cms/</a> in
        your browser.
      </td>
     </tr>

     <tr>
      <td>Login</td>
      <td>
       <span class='login-48 icon-48'/>
      </td>
      <td>
         <a href="./howto/login.html">Login to Hippo CMS</a> in the standard CMS admin account.
      </td>
     </tr>

     <tr>
      <td>Password</td>
      <td>
       <span class='admin-48 icon-48'/>
      </td>
      <td> 
         <a href="./howto/change_password.html">Change the password</a> of the
         admin account.
         <p>
          Instead, you could create another account for yourself and deactivate the standard admin account, but
         you can not delete the standard admin account, so you might as well use it.
     </p>
      </td>
     </tr>

    <tr>
      <td>Deactivate</td>
      <td>
       <span class='admin-48 icon-48'/>
      </td>
      <td>
         <a href="./howto/deactivate_account.html">Deactivate the other standard accounts</a> to
         use personal accounts instead.
         <p>
          Instead, you could just change their passwords, and use them as guest accounts,
          if all your guests are trustworthty.
     </p>

      </td>
     </tr>

     <tr>
      <td>Add Group</td>
      <td>
       <span class='multiuser-48 icon-48'/>
      </td>
      <td>
       <a href="./howto/add_group.html">Add a group</a>. The group will be assigned permissions and
       users as members. All members will have the permissions of the group.
      </td>
     </tr>

     <tr>
      <td>Set Permissions</td>
      <td>
       <span class='multiuser-48 icon-48'/>
      </td>
      <td>
         <a href="./howto/set_permissions_for_group.html">Set permissions for the group</a>.
      </td>
     </tr>

     <tr>
      <td>Add Users</td>
      <td>
       <span class='user-48 icon-48'/>
      </td>
      <td>
         <a href="./howto/add_user.html">Add user account</a>.
      </td>
     </tr>

     <tr>
      <td>Assign membership</td>
      <td>
       <span class='user-48 icon-48'/>
      </td>
      <td>
         <a href="./howto/assign_user_to_group.html">Assign user to group</a>.
      </td>
     </tr>

     <tr>
      <td>Publish All</td>
      <td>
       <span class='user-48 icon-48'/>
      </td>
      <td>
       Because there was already some content that needs to be published, the admin decides to
       <a href="./howto/publish_all.html">Publish them all at once</a>.
      </td>
     </tr>

     <tr>
      <td>Logout</td>
      <td>
       <span class='logout-48 icon-48'/>
      </td>
      <td> 
         <a href="./howto/logout.html">Logout</a>.
      </td>
     </tr>

    </table>
   </blockquote>

    </section>
  </body>
</document>
